title: Awesome Autonomous Drone
detail: Race Drone? Check. Automous Drone? Check.
extended_details: The Awesome Autonomous Drone is going to be a truly unique project in which over the span of a week, a drone is going to be built that can avoid dynamic obstacles, fly certain paths, and land, all autonomously. Oh, and the drone can also be put in to RC mode and be used for racing, because there's no point in having a drone if you can't race it.
